argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Drake=E2=80=99s legal team is led by Willkie Fa=
rr=E2=80=99s <strong>Michael
Gottlieb</strong>, who also happens to be steering <strong>Blake Lively</st=
rong>=E2=80=99s lawsuit depicting <strong>Justin Baldoni </strong>as a sexu=
al predator on the set of <em>It Ends With Us</em>. That conflict escalated=
 last week when Baldoni, flanked by his own retinue, countered with a suit =
that he promised would refute, or at least complicate, some of the accusati=
ons Lively lodged on New Year=E2=80=99s Eve.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin=
-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Baldoni=E2=
=80=99s
voluminous <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z=
1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVaTlwYXNnODV2bGptcVFSbWh6QT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
ZG9jdW1lbnRjbG91ZC5vcmcvZG9jdW1lbnRzLzI1NDk5MzkwLXdheWZhcmVyLz91dG1fY2FtcGF=
pZ249V2hhdCtJJTI3bStIZWFyaW5nJTJCKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MSUyRjIxJTJGMjUlMj=
