line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Late Friday, after a weeklong trial, CNN settle=
d with
<strong>Zachary Young</strong>, the Navy veteran spotlighted in a 2021 expo=
s=C3=A9 on bad actors profiting from aiding Afghans escaping the Taliban. B=
y the time the sides began discussing a deal, a Florida jury had already sl=
apped CNN with a $5 million bill for defamation, teeing up a further round,=
 in which Young=E2=80=99s attorneys gunned for $150 million in punitive dam=
ages=E2=80=94a number calculated after considering CNN=E2=80=99s $4.9 milli=
on in daily revenue and $2 billion-plus =E2=80=9Cnet worth=E2=80=9D (whatev=
er the plaintiff=E2=80=99s
economic expert meant by that). Faced with these stakes, CNN cut its losses=
, promising publicly to mine the ordeal for =E2=80=9Cuseful lessons.=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D=
"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">CNN=E2=80=99s loss isn=E2=80=99t a stunner, a=
lthough many may find it questionable whether the network=E2=80=99s reporte=
rs truly branded Young a <em>criminal</em> war profiteer, as he alleged. CN=
N=E2=80=99s real problem was geographical: The trial was set in Panama City=
, one of Florida=E2=80=99s
deepest-red outposts. Yet what=E2=80=99s truly surprising is how Young=E2=
=80=99s legal team managed to transform this low-key defamation trial into =
a referendum on American journalism. In closing arguments, <strong>Vel Free=
dman</strong>, Young=E2=80=99s attorney, underlined the presence of reporte=
rs in the courtroom and watching the stream remotely, then urged jurors to =
send a message that would ripple across newsrooms everywhere. =E2=80=9CMedi=
a companies are waiting by their phones to see what you do,=E2=80=9D he tol=
d them.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">As deliberations began, CNN=E2=80=99s Ballard S=
pahr team drew Judge <strong>William Henry</strong>=E2=80=99s attention to =
the Supreme Court=E2=80=99s 2007 <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJ=
lbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVaTlwYXNnODV2bGptcVFSbWh6QT0iLCJocm=
VmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9zdXByZW1lLmp1c3RpYS5jb20vY2FzZXMvZmVkZXJhbC91cy81NDkvMzQ2L=
z91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249V2hhdCtJJTI3bStIZWFyaW5nJTJCKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MSUy=
RjIxJTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fY29udGVudD1XaGF0K0klMjdtK0hlYXJpbmclMkIrLStTVUJ=
TQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgxJTJGMTQlMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWxfYWN0aW9uXH=
